The **Quick Tutorial** is a brief walkthrough of a <%= pne %> document window
that highlights its main features. Follow the steps below to activate the
**Quick Tutorial**.
![quick tutorial](all-helper-tutorial)

1. The **Quick Tutorial** starts automatically the first time you use _Balthisar
   Tidy_.

2. You can also activate the **Quick Tutorial** by selecting **Show the Quick
   Tutorial…** in the **Help** menu.
   ![help menu](all-menu-help){: .menu_dropshadow}

3. You can start the **Quick Tutorial** using the **Tutorial** button on the
   document window’s toolbar.
   ![view menu](all-docpart-toolbar)

The **Quick Tutorial** may also appear automatically when you update to a newer
version of <%= pne %>, in order to highlight new features.
{: .tip}